    "details": {
      "alignment": "",
      "race": "",
      "class": "",
      "biography": {
        "value": "<h2>SPECIAL ABILITIES</h2>\n<p><strong>Mobility </strong>Scout gains a +4 bonus to its AC against attacks of opportunity it provokes by leaving a threatened square.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Shot on the Run</strong> As a full action, Scout can move up to its speed, making one ranged attack at any point during its movement.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>DRONE MODS</h2>\n<p><strong>Camera </strong>As long as Scout is within range of Quig&rsquo;s expert rig (5 miles), Quig can see through Scout&rsquo;s senses (in addition to whatever a typical human can see).</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Enhanced Armor</strong> Scout gains +2 to its AC (this has been added to its EAC and KAC above).</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Enhanced Senses</strong> Scout gains low-light vision and darkvision, which also operate through its camera.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Flight System Scout</strong> has a flight system included in its chassis. This grants it the flight listed with its speed.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Hardened AI</strong> Checks to hack Scout take a &ndash;4 penalty.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Weapon Mount</strong> Scout has a corona laser pistol, which can be fired 20 times before Quig must recharge or replace its battery</p>",
