          "short": "",
          "value": "<p>&gt;<a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"sfrpg.class-features\" data-id=\"cQtmz297P5g6g5xv\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Advanced Mods</a></p>\n        <p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl30_LabelName\">Your drone gains a fly speed equal to half its land speed with average maneuverability for up to 10 minutes per day. This duration need not be continuous, but it must be used in 1-minute increments. You can select this mod a second time; in this case, the drone’s fly speed increases to its full land speed, and there is no limit on the amount of time it can fly.</span></p>",
