          "value": "<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.QsCRXffpsDoMvPnT]{Basic Mods}</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl10_LabelName\">Your drone’s AI is secured against outside influence. Any attempt to hack your drone takes a –4 penalty, and your drone receives a +4 insight bonus to saving throws against spells or effects that attempt to take control of the drone or otherwise dictate its actions.</span></p>",
